**When generating a Git commit message, follow EXACTLY these constraints:**

- **Format:** `type(scope): Subject`
- **Allowed `type`:** `feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|test|chore|perf|revert|ci|build|i18n`
- **Required `scope`:** `api|frontend|backend|docs|tests|config|chore|build|deps|auth|db|ui|perf|security`
